performance.of: MIRA baseline and the LSTM models

significant difference.from sentence: There is a significant difference in performance of the MIRA baseline and the LSTM models , both in terms of F1 - score and in accuracy .

More than 30 %.from sentence: More than 30 % of golden compressions could be fully regenerated by the LSTM systems which is in sharp contrast with the 20 % of MIRA .

scores.from sentence: The differences in F- score between the three versions of LSTM are not significant , all scores are close to 0.81 .
